    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "What an understatement.\n\n\nZUBY: (@ZubyMusic)\n\n'The right' is probably going to fracture over the next decade like how 'the left' fractured over the previous one.\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/ZubyMusic/status/1895196658625060960#m",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2033631732860084617",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-16T19:49:22+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "People now need 'studies' to believe things that were obvious to everybody 2,000 years ago.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2032365709376860204",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T07:58:39+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
